@everyone Hi everyone! Sorry for pin you. We recently optimized the latest version of the English translations in an effort to address some issues. Have you noticed any improvements? 

Due to the massive volume of game text, we have decided to adopt a hybrid approach of AI translation combined with manual proofreading to improve the experience for everyone. We are currently recruiting English translators and have started working on this initiative. If you encounter any issues with translations, please report them here—we will address each one individually. Thank you all for your support! We’re especially grateful for the many new members who have recently joined our community. We hope you enjoy the game! 🎮✨

